<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product Unavailable</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .container h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .container p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .container a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .container a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- start header -->

    <!-- end header -->


    <div class="container">
        <h1>Product Currently Unavailable</h1>
        <p>We're sorry, but the product you're looking for is currently unavailable. Please check back later or explore other products in our store.</p>
        <a href="/user/shop">Go to home page</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
